	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The only heat you'll find will be on the voltage regulator/it's heat sink. If you want to do away with heat, get a better regulator which doesn't need a heat sink or get a gigantic fin heatsink. A fan on a NES would be sad, not cool.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


