	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't think changing the regulator would really change heat dissipation power, but for sure a single fan would consume a lot more power than the NES itself.
<br />Overloading the regulator with a fan to cool it makes no sense to me. It is like a little cat that want to catch its own tail.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

